description: Don’t miss out on this stunning redesigned mid-century cottage perfectly situated minutes from the Bishop Arts District in the highly sought out Historical Elmwood Neighborhood. Modernized by Q4 Innovation this Heart of Dallas property offers uncompromising quality, design and detail throughout. This cozy home features 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, and office, lifestyle room with elegant floor to ceiling windows. Boasting a beautiful modern farmhouse design, you will not be disappointed with the open floor concept and luxury finishes. Whether it’s stepping into the tranquility of your very own oversized backyard, taking a short walk to Tyler Station to enjoy a morning yoga class, or catching a beer with friends at the nearby Oak Cliff Beer Garden. This beautiful fully renovated one story home will certainly not last long!!!

description: Gated community approximately 10 minutes east of downtown Dallas. Completely renovated in 2019. Real hardwood floors, full interior paint, flooring, LED lighting, Delta fixtures; custom cabinets in kitchen, bathrooms, and laundry with soft close doors; matching quartz counters in kitchen and baths; brand new roof in 2021 with full exterior paint and caulking; Smart lighting and thermostats; Viking range; office is adjacent to kitchen or could be a 5th bedroom; custom painted garage with epoxy floor. Huge bedrooms! Two walk in attic storage areas. Second living space upstairs with full wet bar and beverage fridge. Very quiet, active community.     Virtual matterport tour available.

description: Contemporary Masterpiece designed by renowned Lionel Morrison on ~2-acre corner lot in Hillcrest Estates. Fully redeveloped 14,795 sq ft home in 2022 by Crescent Estate Custom Homes under design of Brant McFarlin. Flr-ceiling windows, lush landscaping, concrete flrs, lux designer finishes, & lrg exercise room in finished basement. 1st level feat open family, living, & dining rms, bar w wine rm, & rebuilt kitchen w Wolf appliances, new marble countertops, cabinetry, lighting & butler’s pantry overlooking infinity pool.Primary ste w sitting area, 2 custom sep closets, spa bath w updated fixtures, stonework, & lighting, 2 WC & outdoor shower. Also feat private laundry rm & coffee bar. 2nd level w 5 ensuite guest rms, private guest ste w a kitchenette, playrm, lg utility rm, media, & office w fp. Bkyrd w infinity pool w spa, outdoor living w atch grill & FP, grassy yard w trees. 4car garage w rm for lift. Elan Smart Home system for audio,visual, lighting, HVAC, cameras & security.

This beautiful, fully remodeled home will not last. Step into the large bedrooms with walk-in closets and freshen up in the custom porcelain tile showers and fully remodeled bathrooms. Updated windows, newer roof, updated electrical, new HVAC condensers, and more!

description: This pretty mid-century modern home is ready for a new owner. The seller has done the hard updating, now you can come and enjoy! Let me name a few of the upgrades: The home has recently had new paint both on the outside and the inside, the roof has new shingles and the foundation work features a lifetime transferable warranty. The HVAC is new and the water heater is new. Let's not overlook the pretty part of this rehab. Get a look at the kitchen. GREAT new cabinets that reach to the ceiling with pretty shaker doors on them plus subway tile as a backsplash and stunning granite countertops! Do not miss the cabinet pantry for all that good food and appliances you need. The kitchen also features a new stainless dishwasher and stainless gas drop in range. Be sure and checkout the updated bathrooms. The kitchen is complete with ceramic tile on the floor but much of the remainder of the home features new vinyl wood plank flooring. This home may have been built in 1957 but it looks 2022 to me!

description: Designed by Bud Oglesby in 1972.Owners  purchased it in 2005 and undertook massive remodeling project and completed another remodel in 2022.Home has won numerous awards for design excellence and is a modern masterpiece. Comprised of approx 15,918 sf, home has main footprint of around 10,000 sf with 5 bedrooms and multiple living areas.Additional 6,000 sf comprises separate but attached guest suite with 2 bedrooms,living area, another suite for guests,and  3rd suite that may be used as office,exercise,or crafts.There are outdoor loggias and terraces,stunning pool,tennis court,treehouse and a zipline!5 car attached garage.Carriage House, approx 7179 sf, was designed to function as a home to the owner’s numerous race cars as well as entertaining area.The 6 car garage has multiple doors that open the main floor to the landscape of surrounding grounds. There are adjacent living and dining areas,powder baths,elevator to lower level which includes 2 car garage,catering kitchen,simulator room.
